# The @schoen scope (the aislop AI-slop gate, fork build @schoen/aislop with
# C#/roslynator + newer rules) is served from the self-hosted Gitea npm
# registry, not public npm. Read access is anonymous (no token needed).
# Gitea's self-signed (mkcert) cert is trusted in CI via NODE_EXTRA_CA_CERTS
# pointed at the committed .gitea-ca.pem (the public mkcert root CA).
@schoen:registry=https://gitea.llamabox.sticktoitive.net/api/packages/schoen/npm/
